:slide_title Intro to Bootstrap

* Play along by cloning [bootstrapdemo](https://github.com/Cosi-105/bootstrap_demo)

* [Bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com/) is an open source front-end framework
* History: It came from Twitter, and used to be caleld "Twitter Bootstrap" but now it is its own open source project, and is called just "Bootstrap"
* It consists solely of css, javascript, some images, and some fonts
* You should use releae 4 even though it's barely out of beta
* There are various Gems to use Bootstrap with Rails. However use with care, sometimes they create more problems than they solve.
* Look at [Bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com)
* Look at [Bootstrap Demo Github](https://github.com/Cosi-105/bootstrap_demo)
* Checkout [Bootsnipp.com](http://bootsnipp.com) for lots of ideas for bootstrap
